" \"Prepared by the Army Map Service (SX), Corps of Engineers, U.S. Army. Washington, D.C. Copied in 1957 from Virgin Islands, 1:24,000. USGS, Eastern St. Thomas, 1954. Original map compiled by photogrammetric methods from aerial photography dated 1954...\" \"Prepared by the Army Map Service (SX), Corps of Engineers, U.S. Army. Washington, D.C. Copied in 1957 from Virgin Islands, 1:24,000. USGS, Western St. Thomas, 1955. Original map compiled by photogrammetric methods from aerial photography dated 1954...\" Includes text, notes, contour interval diagram, publisher's map list, publisher's coverage map, and color illustration. \"Stock No. E836X16224SW; Stock No. E836X16224SE; Stock No. E836X15221SE.\" Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:49.207Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-01", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-01"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/map59000759/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdsetmaps:ma:p5:90:00:75:9:map59000759:cs000001/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdsetmaps:ma:p5:90:00:75:9:map59000759:cs000001/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=387&w=525", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdsetmaps:ma:p5:90:00:75:9:map59000759:cs000001/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=775&w=1051"], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["saint thomas", "island", "virgin islands", "united states virgin islands", "united states"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["sheet", "map59000759", "2024-02-22t14:53:21", "2025-06-07t22:52:39.900000"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map"], "other_title": ["Standard map series designation: Series A.M.S. E836"], "partof": ["catalog", "geography and map division"], "score": 44.97377, "shelf_id": "G5010 s25 .U5", "site": ["catalog"], "subj